EMBUKU E UNI

(Olkerempe le Nkai 
73  –
89  )

Esipata e Nkai


1  Esipa eisupat Enkai te ilo oitoriori

nkoitoi enyena,

te lelo sidain iltauja.


2  Kake ore ti alo nanu eyieu errorro nkejek aainei,

eyieu eideketari nkejek aainei.


3  Amu aata nanu olom te lelo ooitokoos,

ina kata pee adol nanu dupoto e lelo arruok.


4  Amu meeta ninche emion,

negol naa sidain iseseni lenye.


5  Meeta ninche enyamali anaa enaata iltung'ana,

nemeitamei ninche anaa ilkulikae tung'ana.


6  Ore enkaraki ina, olwuasa ninye

osaei lenye le murt,

olarrabal oimulumul ninche anaa olkila.


7  Etejieita nkonyek enye te mpiron,

netulusoitie mbaa enye aalang iltauja lenye.


8  Neikordodisho ninche, neiro mbaa torrok;

ore te nkitokoos neiro mbaa naaitorogonyie

ilkulikae.


9  Nebol ninche nkutukie enye aaing'orie shumata,

neidapashaki ilng'ejepa lenye enkop.


10  Ore enkaraki ina neibelekenya iltung'ana aaisis ninche;

nemetumie ninche entioto.


11  Nejo ninche, “Kaji eiko Enkai te neyiolou?

Keeta eng'eno Ilo otii Shumata Aisul?”


12  Ng'ura, iltung'ana torrok kulo;

neisikarra ninche anaake,

neponari ninche te karsisisho.


13  Pesho ake nanu aitisinya oltau lai,

naituku nkaik aainei te sinyatisho.


14  Amu ore endama pooki naatooshoki nanu,

naaitamei nkakeny pooki.


15  Naa te najo nanu, “Kalimu kuna,”

anaata maaku asipani te ishoi oo nkera aainei.


16  Naa te nadamu nanu ajo ayiolou kuna,

naa enyamali te nanu.


17  Ore ake pee alo atua ewueji sinyati e Nkai,

namusu taa enkiting'oto enye.


18  Esipa itipika iyie ninche iwuejitin neeideket;

nchoo iyie ninche metabatatata aaidak.


19  Kaji eikunakaki ninche enkidaaroto nabo kata,

eishieki ninche tukul te nkiputukuny.


20  Etiu ninche anaa enkidetidet te neinyototo oltung'ani,

te nidumunye iyie, Olaitoriani,

niwuang'ie ina golon enye.


21  Te netum oltau lai emion,

te neitagori oltau lai,


22  naa kamoda apa nanu mayiolo toki,

natiu apa nanu anaa eng'ues ti alo iyie.


23  Ore ake eyia natii nanu te nebo iyie;

kimbung'a iyie enkaina ai e tatene.


24  Iyie likitorikoyie nanu te nkiguana ino,

ore te siadi niking'amaa nanu te nkitoo ino.


25  Kaing'ae nanu aata te keper leme iyie?

Nemetii ai toki natii oriong enkop nang'uar nanu naadutie.


26  Keidim inkiri osesen lai o ltau lai aaishunye,

kake Enkai e ngolon oltau lai naa erubata ai ntarasi.


27  Amu ng'ura, ore lelo likilamita iyie naa keidak;

inting'ie iyie lelo arruok ti alo iyie.


28  Kake ore nanu eisidai te nataaniki Enkai;

aitaa nanu Olaitoriani Enkai esarunoto ai,

pee atum atolimu isiaaitin inono pooki.

